name: Z- Charged-Up Supersonic Ultra Punch of Justice!
effect: Charge move. Fist Based. On the charge turn, the user raises their Strength by 3. The attack turn of this move has Priority 3 and +1 Accuracy
description: Captain Led focuses his entire might into one single blow, fit for a mighty hero like him. After dealing such a fitting blow, he's left invigorated.
